Package org.nineml.coffeefilter

Class InvisibleXmlFailureDocument

java.lang.Object
org.nineml.coffeefilter.InvisibleXmlDocument
org.nineml.coffeefilter.InvisibleXmlFailureDocument
public class InvisibleXmlFailureDocument extends InvisibleXmlDocument
A failure document represents the results of a failed parse. This is a subclass of the InvisibleXmlDocument that generates the result document for a failed parse.
